java.lang.Object
Transporter<TransportedEntity>
public class Transporter<TransportedEntity extends Transportable>
extends java.lang.Object
A class that contains the functionality to transport object. Usually created as an instance variable in the objects that want to be able to transport a certain TransportedEntity
